modName: Riverside Cabin- a small player home for Riverwood
summary: this adds a small player home just outside riverwood. you can fast travel to the location.
descriptionHtml:
This adds a small house for your player just outside Riverwood. The house contains chests, and other containers (including a wall safe- see images), crafting stations, and a cooking pot.

This is a Standalone mod- no other mods required.
Please send your feedback. more updates and other home versions to come. (may be separate mods)

If you like it, please Endorse! Thanks for your support!
author: recon7773
